QuestData.Title: Mass Production
QuestData.Description: Wahoo!! Did you SEE that?!$b$bWe need to get this into production right away!$b$bHere. Take the rest of the stuff to Jinx. You'll find him setting up our new facility just west of here.
QuestData.LogDescription: Flooz wants you to take Tweedle's Pow-Pow Powder to Jinx at The Skunkworks.
QuestData.RewardText: <Jinx examines the powder carefully for a moment.>$b$bHmmm.$b$bIt'll take a little time. But yes, we can put this into a bomb....
